cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.PL 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.AI - The paper deals with high-level robot controllers, which is a subfield of AI. 
2. cs.RO - The paper specifically mentions robot control languages and their limitations, indicating a focus on robotics. 
3. cs.LO - The paper introduces a logic-based control language and extends the situation calculus, which falls under the subfield of logic. 
4. cs.SE - The paper deals with the execution of actions and the projection of how the world evolves, which are topics related to software engineering. 
5. cs.PL - The paper introduces a new variant of a logic-based control language, which falls under the subfield of programming languages.
